@startuml UC3_HighLevel_Assign_Track_Work_Order
title UC3 — Assign and Track Work Order (High-Level)

skinparam Style strictuml
autonumber

actor Supervisor
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Technician

Notif -> Supervisor : Notify maintenance request

Supervisor -> MMS : Select request and assign technician
MMS -> MMS : Validate assignment
MMS -> MMS : Create work order
MMS -> Notif : Send work order notification
Notif -> Technician : Notify new work order
MMS --> Supervisor : Confirm assignment

Supervisor -> MMS : Track work order status
MMS --> Supervisor : Display work order status

@enduml